frames.caption: A woman adorned with a dark, feathered crown stands gracefully, her eyes closed in serene contemplation. Two ravens, one perched on her shoulder and another near her face, add an air of mystery to the scene. The interplay of shadows and light creates a dramatic and ethereal atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a mystical setting where a woman, possibly a queen or enchantress, is surrounded by ravens. The lighting is low and moody, casting intricate shadows that enhance the mysterious and regal ambiance.
